    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The double VANOS system has been proactively serviced to ensure precise valve timing, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been inspected and reinforced for structural rigidity. The suspension utilizes Bilstein dampers and refreshed polyurethane bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in and lateral stability expected of the chassis. While the car exhibits minor cosmetic road wear, the mechanical powertrain is robust, delivering linear power and a visceral exhaust note. This is a driver-focused machine with a well-documented service history covering critical cooling system and drivetrain maintenance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
