    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and is presented in a well-maintained state that balances performance with practicality. The exterior retains a deep luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with city parking. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats show light bolster wear but remain firm and supportive, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound, having received a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection just last month. It shifts smoothly through all gears and tracks straight on the highway. I have kept a binder of service records to verify its consistent upkeep. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next owner.",
